main event: A civilian reported observing a white oval object in the sky in Miami, Florida, on May 13, 1965.
interesting points: The object was observed for approximately 3 minutes,The course of the object was reported to be straight and level,The observation was made without any physical evidence or photographs,The report concluded that there was insufficient information,The report includes a questionnaire specifically designed for UFO sightings.
witness description: a 33-year-old male who reported the sighting to the President of the Miami UFO Study Group
